      "acceptanceCriteria": "Continuum linear-elastic titanium alloy model with frictional contact at screw-rod interface is appropriate for the load range of interest; geometric nonlinearity enabled.",
      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V implant components modeled as linear elastic (E=114 GPa, nu=0.34) with large-deformation kinematics. Frictional contact (mu=0.2) at screw-rod interface captures load transfer mechanism. UHMWPE test block modeled as bilinear elastic-plastic consistent with F1717 coupon characterization. Model form is consistent with the physical regime of the validation dataset."
