      "rationale": "Titanium alloy elastic modulus and yield strength taken from certified material test reports (MTRs) for the production lot used in the 11 test constructs. UHMWPE block properties from tensile coupon tests performed concurrently. Screw and rod geometry from CMM measurements (±0.005 mm). Torque preload on set screws estimated from calibrated torque wrench records."
